 <span data-ttu-id="5996e-104">この型が所属するグループの一部、 <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRule>、 <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRuleCollection>、および<xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRuleAction>型です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5996e-104">This type is part of a group that includes the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRule>, the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRuleCollection>, and the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRuleAction> types.</span></span>  
  
